<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title>File Metadata Microservice</title>
        <link rel='stylesheet' href='https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.6/css/bootstrap.min.css'>
        <link rel='stylesheet' href='./site.css'>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class='container'>
            <h1>Upload File Microservice</h1>
            <blockquote>
                User Stories
                <ul>
                    <li>I can submit a FormData object that includes a file upload.</li><br>
                    <li>When I submit something, I will receive the file size in bytes within the JSON response.</li>
                </ul>
            </blockquote>
            
            <h2>Application</h2>
            
            <form action='/upload' enctype="multipart/form-data" method='POST'>
                <div class='form-group'>
                    <label>Select a file</label>
                    <input type='file' name='misc_file' class="form-control">
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Upload</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>